12 October 2007Members of the media are invited to a comprehensive briefing by the Directors-General (DGs) of the Economic Cluster, on progress around the cluster's work.The briefing will also profile and highlight work from individual departments, and outline future plans.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: 17 October 2007 (Wednesday) Time: 13h00 Venue: Committee Room 1, Ground Floor, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.RSVP Loedfie Hendricks Cell: 082-670-4145 E-mail: loedfieh@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)